# Repository Language Statistics Override
# This is a Markdown/configuration-based kit, not a traditional application

# Mark ALL file types as vendored to exclude from language statistics
*.sh linguist-vendored
*.py linguist-vendored
*.js linguist-vendored
*.ts linguist-vendored
*.tsx linguist-vendored
*.jsx linguist-vendored
*.json linguist-vendored

# Mark directories as vendored
.claude/ linguist-vendored
.claude-code-router/ linguist-vendored
examples/ linguist-vendored
scripts/ linguist-vendored

# Mark documentation
*.md linguist-documentation